ZH: 这座电厂是我们国家最大的发电厂。
EN: This power plant is the largest in our country.

ZH: 电厂的燃料可以是煤炭、天然气或核能。
EN: The fuel for power plants can be coal, natural gas, or nuclear energy.

ZH: 这家电厂使用先进的设备来产生电力。
EN: This power plant uses advanced equipment to generate electricity.

ZH: 电厂的排放对环境有很大影响。
EN: The emissions from the power plant have a significant impact on the environment.

ZH: 我们的城市需要建设更多的电厂来满足日益增长的电力需求。
EN: Our city needs to build more power plants to meet the growing demand for electricity.

ZH: 这座电厂每天可以生产数百万千瓦的电力。
EN: This power plant can generate millions of kilowatts of electricity every day.

ZH: 电厂的运行受到政府的监管。
EN: The operation of the power plant is regulated by the government.

ZH: 这个项目计划在未来五年内建设一座新的电厂。
EN: This project plans to build a new power plant in the next five years.

ZH: 电厂的建设需要大量的资金和资源。
EN: The construction of a power plant requires a large amount of funding and resources.

ZH: 近年来，我们国家加大了对清洁能源电厂的投资。
EN: In recent years, our country has increased investment in clean energy power plants.

ZH: 电厂的建设引发了当地居民的抗议。
EN: The construction of the power plant has sparked protests from local residents.

ZH: 这座电厂提供了许多就业机会。
EN: This power plant provides many employment opportunities.

ZH: 在建设电厂时需要考虑到周围居民的利益。
EN: The interests of the surrounding residents need to be taken into account when building a power plant.

ZH: 这座电厂已经运营了十年，但仍保持良好的状态。
EN: This power plant has been operating for ten years and is still in good condition.

ZH: 电厂的污染对水和土壤也造成了影响。
EN: The pollution from the power plant also has an impact on water and soil.

ZH: 这座电厂最近发生了一起事故，导致停工一周。
EN: This power plant recently had an accident that resulted in a one-week shutdown.

ZH: 我们正致力于开发更多的可再生能源电厂。
EN: We are committed to developing more renewable energy power plants.

ZH: 这家电厂使用高效的技术来节约能源。
EN: This power plant uses efficient technology to conserve energy.

ZH: 电厂的运行费用占了公司总成本的一大部分。
EN: The operating costs of the power plant account for a large part of the company's total expenses.

ZH: 这座电厂已经成为当地的标志性建筑物。
EN: This power plant has become a landmark in the local area.
